shops, pubs and public places back open, people have started going out and about frequently and honestly, we love to see it. Everyone is busy booking their holidays and vacations, picking out dresses and we’ve come up with one of the most useful and important lists for you. Your summer holiday hair ideas! It can get a little frustrating at times when you can't decide what type of hairstyle goes the best with your outfit, when you're out, at the airport, at a dinner party and so on.. Don't worry we’ve got your back!<br><br>To make it a little easier for you, we’ve separated this post into four parts based on the occasion, place and time</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-29_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-31_">Got to nail that airport look!!&nbsp;</span></h2><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-32_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-33_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-34_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-ed4e3490--154OutfitIdeasforTravelingAirportStyle58_1200x.jpg?v=1627641643" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-ed4e3490--154OutfitIdeasforTravelingAirportStyle58.jpg?v=1627641643 1536w" width="1200" height="1932" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-35_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-36_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-4e3490c9--608e142df77951b5fdbf980a0532d5d4_1200x.jpg?v=1627641675" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-4e3490c9--608e142df77951b5fdbf980a0532d5d4.jpg?v=1627641675 1536w" width="439" height="548" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-37_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-39_">We all have that friend or a family member who wants to reach the airport six hours before a flight! Everyone’s running around and it's getting rushed and you still have to decide how to style your hair because hello who said you can't look cute while travelling.&nbsp;<br><br>Most of the time, people pick up comfortable sweat suits and loungewear while travelling especially when it's a long run to your final destination. We suggest going with a messy bun is the best way to go. Easy, efficient and does the job. You can also twist your hair up and put on a small clutch to give it a more trendy look. Pull out some strands along the side of your face and voila! You're good to go.<br></span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-40_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-41_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-42_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-44_">Take me where the water is</span></h2><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-45_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-47_">Do you know the word that best resonates with Summer? WATER! duh! While you’re out on vacation, a big chunk of your day is spent alongside the pool/beach or doing stuff like cycling, hiking etc. You should keep the hair out of your face while out in the sun or (shade)<br><br><a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-braid-hair-extensions-3-popular-hair-braid-styles" target="_blank">Two top knot braids</a> - Very much in trend right now it's the perfect hairstyle to match it with a swimsuit and beach shorts. It gives off a very chill vibe and keeps the hair out of your face for almost 95% of the day. Amazing, right?&nbsp;<br><br>One single braid - A very protective yet cool enough to spend a day out near the pool hairstyle. You can always experiment in several ways when it comes to a single braid and whatever you think goes <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/how-to-match-your-clothes-to-your-hair" target="_blank">the best with your outfit and face</a> can make you feel like a princess in a castle! We’re not kidding.&nbsp;<br><br><a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/blogs/hair-blog/hair-wrapped-around-ponytail" target="_blank">A High ponytail</a> - Another stunning way to glam up your little beach day out. Keep the hair out of your face and yet pull off a gorgeous Instagram shoot look ;) What more could you want right?&nbsp;<br><br>If you’re wearing extensions or <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-hair-extensions" target="_blank">clip in extensions</a> make sure you take them out before you go ahead and take a dive!&nbsp;</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-48_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-49_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-50_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-d380f0e4--Picture4_1200x.jpg?v=1627623897" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-d380f0e4--Picture4.jpg?v=1627623897 1536w" width="319" height="294" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-51_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-52_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-0fd380f0--Pi